body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting Car Solutions. My name is Anthony Green. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Katherine. How can I assist you today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling frustrated with the data management at your dealership.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand your concern. Could you provide me with your phone number, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, it's five five five, eight seven two, one two three four.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you. And could you also confirm your address for verification purposes?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Of course, it's two zero zero Main Street, Cityville, State ABC, one two three four five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you for providing the information, Katherine. I will look into the data management issue for you. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: No, that's all. Thank you for your help.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: You're welcome, Katherine. Thank you for reaching out to us. Have a great day!
